ed="T" n="0737c21"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0737c21"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042216"><placeName>京師</placeName><placeName>西明寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A008873">良秀</persName>傳（<persName key="A009559">談筵</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0737c22"/><persName key="A008873">釋良秀</persName><ptr target="#n3292"/>，姓<name>郭</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000005165">蒲津</placeName>人也。年及<anchor xml:id="beg0737sgsz8"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic><g ref="#Z1247"/></sic><corr>佩</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0737sgsz8"/>觿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g827"/>，挺然<lb
ed="T" n="0737c23"/>離俗，乃往<placeName key="PL000000005172"><placeName>中條山</placeName><placeName>柏梯<anchor xml:id="beg0737sgsz10"/>寺<anchor xml:id="end0737sgsz10"/></placeName></placeName>披削，誦通經業，<lb
ed="T" n="0737c24"/>受具律儀。誓以傳講為己事，勤苦忘疲。三<lb
ed="T" n="0737c25"/>藏俱尋，九流<ptr type="glossary" target="#g378"/>外贍。于時籍甚<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g691"/>，孰不欽崇。<date from-iso="+0788-02-16" key="j20089172009270" to-iso="+0789-02-03"><name>貞元</name><lb
ed="T" n="0737c26"/>四年</date>，奉詔與<placeName key="PL000000055418">罽賓國</placeName><persName key="A008859">般若<roleName>三藏</roleName></persName>同譯《大乘理<lb
ed="T" n="0737c27"/>趣六波羅蜜經》<ptr target="#n14"/>十卷<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n265"/>。至<date key="j20093042009304" when-iso="+0789-03-09">五年二月四日</date>解座，<lb
ed="T" n="0737c28"/>寫本進過。尋奉<persName key="A004215">德宗</persName>勅令<persName key="A008873">秀</persName>造疏，上表云：<lb
ed="T" n="0737c29"/>「<date key="j20092392009239" when-iso="+0789-01-03">去年十一月二十八日</date>右街功德使<persName key="A008878">王希遷</persName><pb ed="T" n="0738a" xml:id="T50.2061.0738a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0738a01"/>奉宣，令<persName key="A008873">良秀</persName>等修撰新翻《大乘理趣六波羅<lb
ed="T" n="0738a02"/>蜜經疏》者。伏聞至道同源，聖人一貫，<persName key="A002799">大雄</persName>示<lb
ed="T" n="0738a03"/>相，演妙音於<placeName key="PL000000048398">獨園</placeName>，寶位分身，霈湛恩於雙<lb
ed="T" n="0738a04"/>闕。開佛日於聖日，降絲綸於法輪，所以<anchor xml:id="beg0738sgsz1"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0738sgsz1"/><lb
ed="T" n="0738a05"/>化慈航，致人壽域。不然，豈得握真符而契<lb
ed="T" n="0738a06"/>合，應休運<ptr type="glossary" target="#g828"/>以感通？況以此經，<persName key="A002799">如來</persName>之密印，<lb
ed="T" n="0738a07"/>群生之度門，得<placeName key="PL000000023663">白馬</placeName>之寶函，啟<placeName key="PL000000042420">青龍</placeName>之祕<lb
ed="T" n="0738a08"/>藏，是第一義<ptr type="glossary" target="#g474"/>，理去筌蹄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g829"/>，於最後乘<ptr type="glossary" target="#g181"/>說無分<lb
ed="T" n="0738a09"/>別。加以天文煥發，叡思昭回。真如<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g763"/>契心，已闡<lb
ed="T" n="0738a10"/>微於<name>釋</name>氏；般若<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g26"/>製序，諒<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g831"/>纘<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g832"/>文於太宗<ptr target="#n830"/>。慈雲溥<lb
ed="T" n="0738a11"/>潤於大根<ptr target="#n834"/>，湛露垂滋於貝葉。<persName key="A008873">良秀</persName>等材惟<lb
ed="T" n="0738a12"/>末學，性異生知，謬寄討論，伏增殞越<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g835"/>。上承<lb
ed="T" n="0738a13"/>嚴旨，徒側管以窺天；虔奉本師<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g190"/>，懼升堂而<lb
ed="T" n="0738a14"/>鼓瑟。所修撰疏一部，謹附<persName key="A008878">王希遷</persName>隨表奉<lb
ed="T" n="0738a15"/>進，伏乞聖慈，許令同修疏沙門<persName key="A009559">談筵</persName>於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042216">當<lb
ed="T" n="0738a16"/>寺</ref>讚演及流布中外。所冀落落真言，示丹<lb
ed="T" n="0738a17"/>青於新學；明明像教，流粉澤於將來。」<ref type="person" target="#A004215">帝</ref>覽奏，<lb
ed="T" n="0738a18"/>勅內給事<persName key="A009556">毛瑛琦</persName>宣慰<persName key="A008873">良秀</persName>、<persName key="A009559">談筵</persName>、<persName key="A009167">道恒</persName>等：<lb
ed="T" n="0738a19"/>「宜共賜絹九十匹，至可領取。比修《疏義》，甚<lb
ed="T" n="0738a20"/>大勤勞也。秋熱，兼問師等各平安好在。」<persName key="A008873">秀</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0738a21"/>辭筆義端，時少倫匹。終沒罔知時代焉。</p>
